m/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/events/4302959","actor":{"login":"derekjones","id":763613,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjc2MzYxMw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/763613?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/derekjones","html_url":"https://github.com/derekjones","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/derekjones/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/derekjones/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/derekjones/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/derekjones/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/derekjones/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/derekjones/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/derekjones/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/derekjones/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/derekjones/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"event":"subscribed","commit_id":null,"commit_url":null,"created_at":"2011-10-17T15:29:32Z","performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/comments/2431545","html_url":"https://github.com/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/588#issuecomment-2431545","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/588","id":2431545,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDI0MzE1NDU=","user":{"login":"tomcode","id":228003,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIyODAwMw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/228003?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode","html_url":"https://github.com/tomcode","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2011-10-17T16:59:16Z","updated_at":"2011-10-17T16:59:16Z","body":"I got bitten by getwhere, somewhere forgotten in a very old, long forgotten  (super stable 'til now) routine.\n\nI've compared the change log 1.72. to 2.0.0 with the upgrade instructions,here's the list :\n\n# General\n\nPHP 4 support is removed. CodeIgniter now requires PHP 5.1.6.\n\nScaffolding, having been deprecated for a number of versions, has been removed.\n\nThe CAPTCHA plugin has been converted to a Helper and documented.\nThe JavaScript calendar plugin was removed.\n\nThe system/cache and system/logs directories are now in the application directory.\n\nThe deprecated Validation Class has been emoved.\n\n# The config folder\n\nthe follwing files have been changed:\n- config.php\n- database.php\n- mimes.php, see Other Changes further down\n- routes.php\n- user_agents.php\n\nthe follwing files have been added:\n- foreign_chars.php\n- profiler.php\n\n# Libraries\n\nThe xss_clean() function has moved to the Security Class.\n\ndo_xss_clean() now returns FALSE if the uploaded file fails XSS checks.\n\nThe Session Class requires now the use of an encryption key set in the config file.\n\nThe default encryption mode in the Encryption library is now CBC.\n\nInput library mehods post() and get() will return all POST and GET items (respectively) if there are no parameters passed in.\n\n# Database\n\nThe following deprecated functions have been removed: orwhere, orlike, groupby, orhaving, orderby, getwhere.\n\nThe deprecated _drop_database() and _create_database() functions have been removed from the db utility drivers.\n\n# Helpers\n\nThe dohash() function is now deprecated in favour of do_hash() for naming consistency.\n\nThe second parameter of directory_map() in the Directory Helper is modified to accept an integer to specify recursion depth.\n\nThe File Helper delete_files() returns no FALSE on failure.\n\nThe img() function of the HTML helper will now generate an empty string as an alt attribute if one is not provided.\n\nIf CSRF is enabled in the application config file, form_open() will automatically insert it as a hidden field.\n\n# Other Changes\n\nSome DIR_WRITE_MODE constants use no FILE_WRITE_MODE where files and not directories are being operated on.\n\n\"default\" is now a reserved name.\n\nAdded 'application/x-msdownload' for .exe files and ''application/x-gzip-compressed' for .tgz files to config/mimes.php.\n\nAdded audio/mpeg3 as a valid mime type for MP3.\n","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/comments/2431545/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"tomcode","id":228003,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIyODAwMw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/228003?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode","html_url":"https://github.com/tomcode","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomcode/receive